data.description: Nice n Tidy Home In Canyon City On Humbolt!Cute kitchen w/lots of light & tile countertops,  dining room, living room w/pellet stove, 2 bedroom, 1 bath, basement w/bonus room, pantry & laundry, ceiling fans,  linen closet, utility room, vinyl windows, forced air oil furnace, wood, carpet & laminate flooring, composition roof w/gutters,  landscaped, fenced yard, shade trees, plenty of space for your rv and recreational toys, circular graveled driveway, detached garage w/workshop, rock retaining wall, bbq lean too.  $245,000 #1118
